values: Prom is this Saturday and I have no idea what to do with my hair.  i have really long blonde hair and i want to put it in an updo put i don't know how!  any suggestions??

Hey all!  I'm a newbie to this community and I just wanted to introduce myself!!  I swim for the Jerry L Garver YMCA in Columbus OH.  I swim Backstroke and IM... All distances!!  I'm going to nationals in the summer so maybe i'll see some of you there!!

I can't wait for prom!! it's going to be a blast!! I can't wait till May 15th.  I have my dress my date, and my hair appointment. I wish it was today.  After prom were going to King's Island.  I'm so excited!  till later!!

OH YEAH BABY!!!  I cant wait for summer nationals!!  it's gonna be a blast!!  I'm going witha bunch of hot guys from my team and my two best girlfriends!!!  I'm gonna have a great time!!  If you know anyone who's going tell me and i'll see ya there!!!
I hate going back to school.  I wish it was sill spring break!!  I want to go back to hanging out with my friends and waking up late, and not having stupid teachers!!!  oh well you cant win em all!
